Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:56.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聖ジョージの聖域を\N第２段階へと移行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:59.02,Default,Index,0,0,0,,Eli Eli Lama Sabachthani?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:59.02,Note,Index,0,0,0,,"My God, my God, why have you forsaken me?" (Matthew 27:45-46)
